{"tid":770641,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone 被其他apps認左做Jailbroken device","createTime":"2018-08-07T09:27:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T16:32:16.000Z","uid":3894,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"43a30da7c269db2cc3752a6bb6e5e76bc57e3cf8","tid":770641,"uid":3894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T09:27:08.000Z","msg":"小弟之前係iOS 8 jailbreak過<br />\n升到iOS 10.3.1就已經冇搞過jailbreak既野了<br />\n但被其他apps好似銀行app block左<br />\n因為佢detect到我既device jailbroken<br />\n有冇巴打知個app係點樣分係咪jailbroken ?<br />\n我上網望過<br />\n我用ifunbox check 過device 入面冇<br />\n- /Applications/<a href=\"http://Cydia.app\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FCydia.app&d=Ny7N15NCh6ivWUs84%2FdG5v9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=dc3fdd6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Cydia.app</a><br />\n- /Library/MobileSubstrate/MobileSubstrate.dylib<br />\n- /bin/bash<br />\n- /usr/sbin/sshd<br />\n- /etc/apt<br />\n- /private/var/lib/apt<br />\n- /private/jailbreak.txt<br />\n亦都打開唔到 cydia://package/com.example.package<br />\n<br />\n求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0176622f225ebaff7462d267caceea80fa2fbd6","tid":770641,"uid":3894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T09:32:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9365cad959f697a034aadc80b25408260908d433","tid":770641,"uid":3894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T01:11:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"577a6e4d90be3b689ba5f53c72bb54e5e0379b55","tid":770641,"uid":3894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T01:50:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"779e32cd3b7d39e0e5af853c51b8e06b396339b8","tid":770641,"uid":83499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T08:21:00.000Z","msg":"reset iphone一次就ok"},{"pid":"9e01c44f7f1415d920cc405cfe85dd511825d786","tid":770641,"uid":23063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T16:32:16.000Z","msg":"宜家仲有冇得 dfu